### 🔌 Backend API (Go)

RESTful JSON API on port 8080. Serve the built React app as static files from the same port.

Endpoints needed:
- `POST /api/auth/login` — returns JWT token
- `POST /api/auth/register`
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/filaments`
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/printers`
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/orders`
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/products` (blueprints/BOM)
- `GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/maintenance`
- `GET /api/reports/financial`
- `GET/PUT /api/settings`
- `POST /api/calculator/compute` — accepts print params, returns cost breakdown

Use JWT middleware for protected routes. CORS enabled for dev.

